"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-comment-columnists-ann-widdecombe-1938347-paris-olympics-last-supper-christians-protest\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Everybody knows how the opening ceremony at the Paris 2024 Olympics contained a depiction of The Last Supper in mockery of millions of watching Christians.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 146, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.995604170884071, \"rank\": 0.004224430105810667, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everybody\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 9}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 20, \"to\": 40}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 59, \"to\": 67}, {\"ngram\": \"a depiction\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 89}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 93, \"to\": 108}, {\"ngram\": \"mockery\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 119}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What is not known at all is the disgraceful action of the French government when a small group of Christians decided to stage a protest.\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9676762855318491, \"rank\": 0.01722315989755045, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.995604170884071, \"rank\": 0.004224430105810667, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the disgraceful action\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 208}, {\"ngram\": \"a small group\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 252}, {\"ngram\": \"a protest\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They hired a bus bearing the slogan \\\"stop attacks on Christians\\\".\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.995604170884071, \"rank\": 0.004224430105810667, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bus\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"the slogan\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 330}, {\"ngram\": \"attacks\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was of course nothing unlawful about such an activity and the bus was driven around Paris attracting many waves and signs of agreement.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996862621211, \"rank\": 3.1373795231615133e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"such an activity\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 420}, {\"ngram\": \"the bus\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"many waves\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"signs\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"agreement\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Naturally there was a large police presence in the city centre and the bus drove past hundreds of French police with no intervention at all.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 601, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2060472127360527e-27, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a large police presence\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"the city centre\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"the bus\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 577}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"no intervention\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This carried on all morning but later that afternoon the bus was flagged down at gunpoint and armed police surrounded the vehicle!\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bus\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"gunpoint\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"armed police\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"the vehicle\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The occupants were arrested for \\\"organising a demonstration\\\" without the approval of the French government.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9676762855318491, \"rank\": 0.01722315989755045, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The occupants\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"a demonstration\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the approval\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was rot as they had already researched the law and definitively established that such regulations applied to large scale marches not a slogan on a bus.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the law\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"such regulations\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"large scale marches\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"a bus\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet they were handcuffed, taken to a secure facility and had all their belongings confiscated.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a secure facility\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"all their belongings\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were then strip searched and refused access to lawyers.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"strip\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"lawyers\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kept in custody overnight, some of them were refused food and water (welcome to Third World France) and also the ability to contact families (welcome to the French Stasi).\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Third_World\", \"score\": 0.9999999957422006, \"rank\": 4.2576989060229725e-09, \"text\": \"Third World\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Third_World\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Third_World\"}, {\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"score\": 0.6145336177343976, \"rank\": 0.39198548506313025, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9676762855318491, \"rank\": 0.01722315989755045, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stasi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stasi\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stasi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stasi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"custody\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"also the ability\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"families\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day they were finally released after prosecutors ruled what everybody had known all along: no offence had been committed.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"prosecutors\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"no offence\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sources have suggested that the intervention was political and it does seem the only plausible explanation, but what worries me is the way this outrage has been ignored by the entire British press and media.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9664151575488898, \"rank\": 0.026135221946139212, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sources\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"the intervention\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"the only plausible explanation\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"this outrage\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"media\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know for a fact that one high circulation Sunday paper had all the details but decided the story was not worth even a few lines.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fact\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"one high circulation\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday paper\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"all the details\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, naturally!\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, it was only a bunch of devout Christians, so who cares?\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.995604170884071, \"rank\": 0.004224430105810667, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only a bunch\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What right have they to free speech?\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What right\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"speech\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, they are probably suing, so we may get some answers to those questions.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some answers\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"those questions\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH CONNECT WITH US TODAY'S PAPER See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2181, \"end\": 2194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Da